relaxed\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"Go to your Dashboard and click on 'Profile.' From there, you can update your display name, profile photo, bio, skills, city, and other personal information. A complete and well-maintained profile helps you build trust with other users and increases your chances of being selected for tasks or attracting buyers to your listings.\\\"}]]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$L2d\\\",\\\"1\\\",{\\\"value\\\":\\\"account-settings-1\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$L2e\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"px-6 text-left\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"How do I get verified on PostAll?\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$L2f\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"px-6 text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"To get verified, go to your Profile page and click the 'Get Verified' button. You'll need to provide a valid government-issued ID and complete our verification process. Verified users receive a special badge on their profile, which increases trust and visibility. Verification is free and typically completes within 24-48 hours after submission.\\\"}]]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$L2d\\\",\\\"2\\\",{\\\"value\\\":\\\"account-settings-2\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$L2e\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"px-6 text-left\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"Can I change my email address or phone number?\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$L2f\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"px-6 text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"Yes, you can update your email address and phone number from the Settings page in your Dashboard. You'll need to verify your new contact information before the change takes effect. We recommend keeping your contact information current to ensure you don't miss important notifications about tasks, messages, and payments.\\\"}]]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$L2d\\\",\\\"3\\\",{\\\"value\\\":\\\"account-settings-3\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$L2e\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"px-6 text-left\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"How do I delete my account?\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$L2f\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"px-6 text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"To delete your account, go to Settings and scroll to the 'Danger Zone' section at the bottom of the page. Click 'Delete Account' and confirm your decision. Please note that account deletion is permanent and cannot be undone. Any active tasks or escrow funds will need to be resolved before deletion can proceed. We recommend withdrawing any remaining wallet balance first.\\\"}]]}]]}]}]}]]}]\\n\"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"17:[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",\\\"safety\\\",{\\\"id\\\":\\\"safety\\\",\\\"className\\\":\\\"mb-12 scroll-mt-24\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-6\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"h-10 w-10 rounded-lg bg-rose-100 text-rose-700 flex items-center justify-center\\\",\\\"children\\\":[\\\"$\\\",\\\"svg\\\",null,{\\\"ref\\\":\\\"$undefined\\\",\\\"xmlns\\\":\\\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\\",\\\"width\\\":24,\\\"height\\\":24,\\\"viewBox\\\":\\\"0 0 24 24\\\",\\\"fill\\\":\\\"none\\\",\\\"stroke\\\":\\\"currentColor\\\",\\\"strokeWidth\\\":2,\\\"strokeLinecap\\\":\\\"round\\\",\\\"strokeLinejoin\\\":\\\"round\\\",\\\"className\\\":\\\"lucide lucide-shield h-5 w-5\\\",\\\"aria-hidden\\\":\\\"true\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"path\\\",\\\"oel41y\\\",{\\\"d\\\":\\\"M20 13c0 5-3.5 7.5-7.66 8.95a1 1 0 0 1-.67-.01C7.5 20.5 4 18 4 13V6a1 1 0 0 1 1-1c2 0 4.5-1.2 6.24-2.72a1.17 1.17 0 0 1 1.52 0C14.51 3.81 17 5 19 5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1z\\\"}],\\\"$undefined\\\"]}]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"h2\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"text-2xl font-bold\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"Safety\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"text-sm text-muted-foreground\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"Staying safe on the platform and protecting yourself\\\"}]]}]]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"data-slot\\\":\\\"card\\\",\\\"className\\\":\\\"bg-card text-card-foreground flex flex-col gap-6 rounded-xl border py-6 shadow-sm\\\",\\\"children\\\":[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"data-slot\\\":\\\"card-content\\\",\\\"className\\\":\\\"p-0\\\",\\\"children\\\":[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$L2c\\\",null,{\\\"type\\\":\\\"single\\\",\\\"collapsible\\\":true,\\\"className\\\":\\\"w-full\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$L2d\\\",\\\"0\\\",{\\\"value\\\":\\\"safety-0\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$L2e\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"px-6 text-left\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"How do I report suspicious activity or a user?\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$L2f\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"px-6 text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"You can report any listing, profile, message, or user by clicking the flag icon or 'Report' button available throughout the platform. Provide as much detail as possible about the issue. Our safety team reviews all reports within 24 hours and takes appropriate action, which may include warnings, account suspension, or permanent bans depending on the severity.\\\"}]]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$L2d\\\",\\\"1\\\",{\\\"value\\\":\\\"safety-1\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$L2e\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"px-6 text-left\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"What are Safe Spots and how do I use them?\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$L2f\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"px-6 text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"Safe Spots are pre-vetted, public meeting locations recommended for in-person transactions. You can find them using our Safe Spots tool, which shows verified locations on a map with ratings and reviews from other users. Safe Spots typically include well-lit areas with CCTV coverage, high foot traffic, and security presence. We strongly recommend using Safe Spots for all in-person meetups.\\\"}]]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$L2d\\\",\\\"2\\\",{\\\"value\\\":\\\"safety-2\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$L2e\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"px-6 text-left\\\",\\\"childr